    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业IoT场景的数据流图。核心是从ActuatorController开始，它会产生TelemetryStream。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，ActuatorController作为起点，直接输出到TelemetryStream。这里用实线箭头表示数据流向对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，用粗实线。而且第一个TelemetryStream会触发第二个TelemetryStream，形成链式处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经连好了B到C的流。接下来C要连到哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "C要连到一个判断节点，还是ActuatorController，但这时候它要做一个决策——检查数据是否满足下发指令的条件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "所以D是个菱形判断框？名字叫ActuatorController，但功能是决策？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，D是决策节点。如果判断为Yes，就走E分支，E还是ActuatorController，表示执行具体控制指令。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Yes分支画好了，E之后继续流出TelemetryStream到F对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，F再到G，然后G要连到EdgeNode，这是现场的数据汇聚点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "EdgeNode画好了，标记为H。H之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "H要再发一个TelemetryStream到I，然后I要回流到D那个判断节点，形成闭环。这是关键——边缘节点要把处理结果反馈给控制器做下一轮决策。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "闭环画好了，I回到D。那D的No分支呢？不满足条件时怎么处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "No分支走J，J也是ActuatorController，但走异常处理或静默分支，然后J直接连到K，K是另一个EdgeNode，用于上报异常状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "No分支和异常路径都画好了。我检查一下，D到E是Yes，D到J是No，两个分支都标了条件。",
